             was indicted for <rs id="t17870711-55-off245" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17870711-55-off245" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870711-55-off245" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t17870711-55-cd246" type="crimeDate">5th of July</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17870711-55-off245 t17870711-55-cd246"></join>, two pieces of dimity, containing seventy-two yards, value 6 l. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17870711-55-victim487" type="victimName">
                           George 
                           Gill
                        <interp inst="t17870711-55-victim487" type="surname" value="Gill"></interp>
