                  , in their dwelling house
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17870711-55-person490">
                  GEORGE
                   GILL
               <interp inst="t17870711-55-person490" type="surname" value="GILL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870711-55-person490" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17870711-55-person490" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
